novika create - a tool for scaffolding Novika applications and libraries

Syntax:

  novika create/[app, lib]

Examples:

  Scaffold a new Novika application:
    $ mkdir example
    $ cd example
    $ novika create/app

  Scaffold a new Novika library:
    $ mkdir example
    $ cd example
    $ novika create/lib
